data.description: New and improved price! Located in the heart of Vancouver, this renovated home is cozy and move-in ready. You'll enjoy the modern kitchen that's bright, open and has great natural light throughout. Remodeled in 2020, the kitchen features stainless steel appliances with a gas range. This charming home offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bath and a living room. The primary bedroom has sliding glass doors to the outdoor covered patio. The large backyard is fully fenced with mature landscaping. Check out the detached one car garage with additional room for a potential office or shop. Conveniently located to grocery shopping, boutiques, markets, schools and offers easy access to the freeways. What my clients loved about their home, "Our cherished home held a special place in my heart, and I'll forever treasure the countless memories we created within its walls. The quaint house exuded character, each room telling a story of our growing family. The neighborhood, with its warm community and friendly neighbors, felt like an extended family itself. The peaceful cemetery behind the house added a unique serenity, serving as a tranquil backdrop to our daily lives. Leaving this haven was bittersweet; the echoes of laughter, the warmth of shared moments, and the character-filled walls will be dearly missed. It was more than a house; it was a nurturing haven for our growing family."
